FBIS3-54198 "drnes015_m_94014" FBIS-NES-94-015 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 JORDAN King Husayn Sends Condolences to Syria's al-Asad JN2101202694 Amman Jordan Television Network in English 2000 GMT 21 Jan 94 JN2101202694 Amman Jordan Television Network Language: English Article Type:BFN [From the "News at Ten" program] [Text] His majesty the king sent a letter of condolence to Syrian President Hafiz al-Asad over the death of his son Basil. The king expressed his deep sorrow and said that only the long distance has prevented him from being with President al-Asad to share with him his pain and the loss of his son.
